        },
        {
          "name": "Collect Metrics",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } },
              "raw": "{\n  \"host\": \"{{PGSQL_PROXY_HOST}}\",\n  \"port\": {{PGSQL_PROXY_PORT}},\n  \"node_host\": \"{{PGSQL_PRIMARY_IP}}\",\n  \"user\": \"postgres\",\n  \"password\": \"\",\n  \"database\": \"postgres\",\n  \"ssl_mode\": \"disable\",\n  \"connect_timeout\": 10,\n  \"patroni_port\": 8008,\n  \"categories\": [],\n  \"limit\": 20\n}"
            },
            "description": "Collects live metrics from a running PostgreSQL/Patroni cluster.\n\n**Required:** `host`, `user`\n\n**Connection routing:**\n- `host` + `port` — HAProxy address; all PostgreSQL queries go through here\n- `node_host` — direct IP of the primary node; used for Patroni REST (`cluster`, `failover` categories). Falls back to `host` when omitted.\n\n**Optional:** `port` (default 5432), `password`, `database` (default `postgres`), `ssl_mode` (`disable`|`require`, default `disable`), `connect_timeout` (seconds, default 10), `patroni_port` (default 8008), `limit` (top-N for slow queries/latency, default 20), `from`/`to` (ISO 8601, filter failover events and slow queries)\n\n**`categories`** — empty array returns all; pick any subset:\n- `cluster` — Patroni HA state, DCS health, node roles, TTL/loop_wait\n- `uptime` — PostgreSQL process uptime\n- `failover` — Patroni timeline/failover history (supports `from`/`to` filter)\n- `connections` — active, idle, idle-in-transaction, lock-waiters, wait-event breakdown\n- `replication` — streaming lag (LSN pipeline), standby count, WAL config, slot lag\n- `performance` — TPS, cache hit ratio, temp files, checkpoint pressure, bgwriter stats\n- `query` — avg/p95/p99 latency, slow queries, lock/deadlock counts, scan efficiency\n- `maintenance` — autovacuum workers, XID wraparound age, logical slot lag, pg_locks",
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://{{API_HOST}}:{{API_PORT}}/cluster/pgsql/metrics",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": ["{{API_HOST}}"],
              "port": "{{API_PORT}}",
              "path": ["cluster", "pgsql", "metrics"]
            }
          }
        },
